BEGIN_TEXT

Find a basis of the subspace of \({\mathbb R}^4\) that consists of all vectors perpendicular to both 
$BR
\{ mbox( display_matrix([[1], [0], [$a], [$b]]), ' and ', display_matrix([[0], [1], [$c], [$d]]), '.' ) \}
$BR 
\{ mbox( ans_array(4,1,5), ', ', ans_array_extension(4,1,5), '.' ) \} 

END_TEXT

